Package: libubuntu-location-service0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A location service aggregating position/velocity/heading
 updates and exporting them over dbus.
 .
 Contains the shared library needed by client applications.

Package: libubuntu-location-service-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libubuntu-location-service0,
	 ${misc:Depends}
Description: A location service aggregating position/velocity/heading
 updates and exporting them over dbus.
 .
 Contains header files required to develop clients talking to the ubuntu location service.

